headline: Xylem Gears Up to Post Q4 Earnings: Here's What's in Store
summary: XYL's fourth-quarter results are likely to reflect the impacts of weakness in the Applied Water segment and input cost inflation. Strength in the M&CS segment is likely to have been a positive.
